/*
  # Complete Field Figures Reseed - Part 1: Grovfelt Standing (B-series) and Circles (C-series)

  This is part 1 of a complete reseed of the field_figures table with correct
  DFS (Det frivillige Skyttervesen) figure data including professional SVGs.

  1. Actions
    - Deactivates ALL existing figures
    - Upserts B45, B65, B100 (standing grovfelt figures)
    - Upserts C20, C25, C30, C35, C40, C50 (circle grovfelt figures)
    - Each upsert uses ON CONFLICT(code) to preserve existing row IDs and FK references

  2. Important Notes
    - SVG data is from professional vector illustrations (Layer_1 / Illustrator style)
    - All figures include proper metadata: dimensions, distances, shape types
    - This migration is idempotent and safe to re-run
*/

